And after 10 hours in newborns there was a total atrophy of the instincts.
The chicks did not react to light or sound.
And the misfortune was that after four days they simply died.
"And twice we managed to hatch the chicks, but then we stopped because it was impossible to work with them there," says Vladimir Sychev about the failure of the experiment with the chicks in space.
