The three cities will connect at the end of the evening via videoconference to jointly sing The Tap Tap's song "End of the World, Cancelled."
The aim of the concert is to raise the necessary resources to finance multifunctional equipment for the STUDEO barrier-free educational center in Jedličkův ústav in Prague, the cost of which amounts to CZK 25 million.
